<!-- features/housing.php -->

<p>Player housing will be easily decorated, useful for storage, and highly available.</p>
<p>In urban centers, apartments will be available for rent. These apartments will have restrictions on customization and higher storage limits.</p>
<p>In the suburbs, houses can be bought, from players or from the municipality. Houses can be built on empty lots. These houses will be larger, with more storage space, and more customization available. Gardens can be placed for small farming.</p>
<p>In the country, farms of varying sizes can be established. The larger the farm, the more intensive the upkeep.</p>